      "content": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n<meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n<meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n<title>LYF 新疆葵花籽（30g*10包）</title>\n<style>\n    body {\n        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;\n        margin: 0;\n        background-color: #fdf5e6;\n        color: #333;\n    }\n    header {\n        background-color: #d84315;\n        color: white;\n        padding: 15px;\n        text-align: center;\n        font-size: 1.5em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    header span {\n        font-size: 1em;\n        font-weight: normal;\n    }\n    .container {\n        max-width: 1200px;\n        margin: auto;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    .product {\n        display: flex;\n        flex-wrap: wrap;\n        background-color: white;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        padding: 20px;\n        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    .product img {\n        max-width: 100%;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .product-info {\n        flex: 1;\n        padding: 20px;\n    }\n    .price {\n        color: #d84315;\n        font-size: 1.8em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    .old-price {\n        text-decoration: line-through;\n        color: #888;\n        margin-left: 10px;\n        font-size: 1em;\n    }\n    .promo-tag {\n        display: inline-block;\n        background-color: #ff5722;\n        color: white;\n        padding: 5px 10px;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        margin-top: 10px;\n        font-size: 0.9em;\n        animation: blink 1s infinite;\n    }\n    @keyframes blink {\n        50% {opacity: 0.5;}\n    }\n    .buy-section {\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n    .buy-section input {\n        width: 50px;\n        text-align: center;\n    }\n    .buy-button, .cart-button {\n        background-color: #ff5722;\n        color: white;\n        padding: 10px 20px;\n        border: none;\n        border-radius: 4px;\n        cursor: pointer;\n        margin-right: 10px;\n        font-size: 1em;\n        font-weight: bold;\n        transition: background-color 0.3s;\n    }\n    .buy-button:hover, .cart-button:hover {\n        background-color: #e64a19;\n    }\n    .recommendations, .comments {\n        background-color: white;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n        padding: 20px;\n        box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        margin-bottom: 20px;\n    }\n    .recommendations .item {\n        display: inline-block;\n        width: 200px;\n        margin: 10px;\n        vertical-align: top;\n    }\n    .recommendations img {\n        width: 100%;\n        border-radius: 8px;\n    }\n    .item-name {\n        font-size: 1em;\n        margin-top: 5px;\n    }\n    .item-price {\n        color: #d84315;\n        font-weight: bold;\n    }\n    .comment {\n        border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;\n        padding: 10px 0;\n    }\n    .comment:hover {\n        background-color: #fff3e0;\n    }\n    footer {\n        background-color: #d84315;\n        color: white;\n        text-align: center;\n        padding: 20px;\n        margin-top: 20px;\n    }\n    @media (max-width: 768px) {\n        .product { flex-direction: column; }\n    }\n    #loading-bar {\n        position: fixed;\n        top: 0;\n        left: 0;\n        height: 4px;\n        background: #ff5722;\n        animation: load 2s linear forwards;\n    }\n    @keyframes load {\n        from { width: 0; }\n        to { width: 100%; }\n    }\n</style>\n</head>\n<body>\n<div id=\"loading-bar\"></div>\n<header>\n    LYF 新疆葵花籽 <span>春节团聚佳品</span>\n</header>\n<div class=\"container\">\n    <div class=\"product\">\n        <div class=\"product-image\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/400x400.png?text=LYF+新疆葵花籽\" alt=\"新疆葵花籽\">\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"product-info\">\n            <h1>LYF 新疆葵花籽（30g*10包）</h1>\n            <p>精选新疆葵花籽，粒粒饱满，香脆可口，适合春节家庭团聚零食。</p>\n            <p class=\"price\">¥16.9 <span class=\"old-price\">¥22.9</span></p>\n            <span class=\"promo-tag\">限时抢购</span>\n            <p>库存：<span id=\"stock\">999</span> 包</p>\n            <div class=\"buy-section\">\n                购买数量：\n                <button onclick=\"changeQty(-1)\">-</button>\n                <input type=\"number\" id=\"qty\" value=\"1\" min=\"1\">\n                <button onclick=\"changeQty(1)\">+</button>\n                <p>单价：¥16.9</p>\n                <p>总价：<span id=\"total\">¥16.9</span></p>\n                <p>预计配送时间：<span id=\"delivery\">3-5天</span></p>\n                <button class=\"cart-button\" onclick=\"addToCart()\">加入购物车</button>\n                <button class=\"buy-button\" onclick=\"buyNow()\">立即购买</button>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"recommendations\">\n        <h2>推荐产品</h2>\n        <div class=\"item\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x200.png?text=瓜子A\" alt=\"\">\n            <div class=\"item-name\">原味瓜子 500g</div>\n            <div class=\"item-price\">¥15.9</div>\n            <button class=\"buy-button\">购买</button>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"item\">\n            <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/200x200.png?text=瓜子B\" alt=\"\">\n            <div class=\"item-name\">焦糖瓜子 300g</div>\n            <div class=\"item-price\">¥12.9</div>\n            <button class=\"buy-button\">购买</button>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"comments\">\n        <h2>用户评论</h2>\n        <div class=\"comment\" title=\"热销评论\">★★★★★ 味道非常香，春节必备！</div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">★★★★☆ 好吃，包装精美。</div>\n        <div class=\"comment\">★★★☆☆ 一般吧，稍微有点咸。</div>\n    </div>\n</div>\n<footer>\n    支付方式：支付宝 | 微信支付<br>\n    物流：顺丰、京东快递<br>\n    预估送达：下单后 3-5 天\n</footer>\n<script>\n    function changeQty(num) {\n        let qtyInput = document.getElementById('qty');\n        let qty = parseInt(qtyInput.value) + num;\n        if (qty < 1) qty = 1;\n        qtyInput.value = qty;\n        updateTotal();\n    }\n    function updateTotal() {\n        let qty = parseInt(document.getElementById('qty').value);\n        let total = (16.9 * qty).toFixed(2);\n        document.getElementById('total').innerText = '¥' + total;\n    }\n    function addToCart() {\n        alert('已加入购物车！');\n    }\n    function buyNow() {\n        alert('跳转到结算页面');\n    }\n    window.onload = () => {\n        setTimeout(() => {\n            document.getElementById('loading-bar').style.display = 'none';\n        }, 2000);\n    }\n</script>\n</body>\n</html>"
